-- Researcher Says China Should Lower Bank Reserve Requirement, News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-23T04:34:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/researcher-says-china-should-lower-bank-reserve-requirement-news-reports.html

          
          
             China should lower its reserve
requirement for the nation’s banks, the Financial News reported
today, citing Wang Songqi, deputy director of financial research
at the Chinese Academy of Social Sciences. The Financial News
newspaper is published by China’s central bank.  
